{"tid":2368016,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB高層曾勵珍開香檳中頭獎 劉丹成為民選「大叔部長」不抗拒演BL","createTime":"2021-01-15T21:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T08:14:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e9322970f46d25c0a4742bad72cb8234ce896915","tid":2368016,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T21:16:12.000Z","msg":"早前ViuTV買2018年爆紅的BL日劇《大叔的愛》版權，打算翻拍成港版《大叔的愛》，部長黑澤武藏由黃德斌主演，主角春田創一及牧凌太這對CP就由Mirror成員Edan和Anson Lo演出，不少網民認為劉丹才是「大叔部長」最佳人選。<br />\n<br />\n問到會否接受BL主題，劉丹並不太抗拒：「唔可以只睇主題，要睇劇情寫啲咩，如果太過份，好似我哋呢啲年紀就唔適合演呢類劇。如果係搞笑劇情都可以，唔係唔想演，總之唔可以演一啲過唔到自己嗰關，我哋做演員無論演咩戲，如果劇情適合自己演一演亦無妨。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210115/ORJ2JMZBOZG5JGSLVTYZ27BCLM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210115%2FORJ2JMZBOZG5JGSLVTYZ27BCLM%2F&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyA3kfWbBCvxMfTTNG0K1D1Y%3D&h=8b307fc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210115%2FORJ2JMZBOZG5JGSLVTYZ27BCLM%2F&h=3470a2f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210115/ORJ2JMZBOZG5JGSLVTYZ27BCLM/</a>"},{"pid":"795f4d1e2eb334045c5abf923b8032bf921575e8","tid":2368016,"uid":256837,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T21:24:14.000Z","msg":"阿爺部長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcec0d191926b621d6d7c213f62a7b30596d33ad","tid":2368016,"uid":264073,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T21:24:34.000Z","msg":"關tvb咩事"},{"pid":"76d13b4c14a4fe9f2070e673b7b733bfe1305aea","tid":2368016,"uid":284183,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T21:36:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">塊西老撚到......................</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff8f7eaf93ab1da187b1786f364484cb255a618","tid":23